            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am still going here, and by far it’s amazing! I’ve read a few reviews, saying that senior school is a bit.. not exactly pleasant. So, not really looking forward to that, but overall, my experience was great! I took one star away because they give us a lot of homework, and you can’t really have fun with that. But overall, good school! And plus I haven’t seen ANY BULLYING here so, definitely recommend sending your kids here! :)",
